  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Reducing prevalence of forced labour in informal RMG factories in Bangladesh by promoting sustainable livelihood opportunities to people through alternative learning pathways.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">BRAC will deliver targeted and evidence-based rights awareness training and skilling for vulnerable workers in source and destination communities, and begin to engage informal factory owners on improving conditions for workers. The project will generate evidence to inform a policy brief to support the longer-term objective of generating government regulation of the informal sector.</narrative>
